## ai_goal_changes
SQL:
```
SELECT match_id, COUNT(*) AS ai_goal_changes FROM events WHERE event_type = 'AG' GROUP BY match_id

## event_counts
SQL:
```
SELECT event_type, COUNT(*) AS count FROM events GROUP BY event_type

## low_shot_levels
SQL:
```
SELECT level_name, COUNT(*) AS matches FROM ( SELECT m.id, m.level_name, SUM(ps.shots_attempted) AS shots FROM matches m JOIN player_stats ps ON ps.match_id = m.id GROUP BY m.id ) WHERE shots <= 5 GROUP BY level_name ORDER BY matches DESC
```

level_name | matches
--- | ---
_No rows_

## per_level_summary
SQL:
```
SELECT m.level_name, COUNT(DISTINCT m.id) AS matches, AVG(m.score_left + m.score_right) AS goals_per_match, SUM(ps.shots_attempted) AS shots_attempted, SUM(ps.shots_made) AS shots_made, AVG(CASE WHEN m.score_left + m.score_right = 0 THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS scoreless_rate, AVG(ps.avg_shot_quality) AS avg_shot_quality FROM matches m JOIN player_stats ps ON ps.match_id = m.id GROUP BY m.level_name ORDER BY scoreless_rate DESC, shots_attempted ASC
```

level_name | matches | goals_per_match | shots_attempted | shots_made | scoreless_rate | avg_shot_quality
--- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | ---
Skyway | 5 | 0.8000 | 57 | 3 | 0.6000 | 0.4221
Pursuit Arena | 5 | 0.4000 | 60 | 1 | 0.6000 | 0.4272
Pursuit Arena 2 | 5 | 0.6000 | 40 | 2 | 0.4000 | 0.4068
Slopes | 4 | 1.7500 | 44 | 7 | 0.2500 | 0.3914
Open Floor | 5 | 2.0000 | 61 | 10 | 0.0000 | 0.4281
